title: How.to.Lose.Friends.and.Alienate.People.Script.Screenplay
description:
The script for the new movie starring Simon Pegg, Megan Fox, Kirsten Dunst, Gillian Anderson, and Jeff Bridges.  Written by Peter Straughan & Toby Young and directed by Robert B. Weide.

A British writer struggles to fit in at a high-profile magazine in New York. Based on Toby Young&#039;s memoir "How to Lose Friends & Alienate People".
